tafsir[6]{c,v,t}:
  109,1,"Maaku-aan nelaaɗo-eehey mon mon yedduɓe Alla."
  109,2,"Mi rewatah jooni wonah ko arata ko ndewaton ko e sanamuuji."
  109,3,"Onon ne on ndewatah Mbo ndewat Mi O, ko Oon woni Alla."
  109,4,"Mi wonah dewoowo ko ndewɗon e sanamuuji."
  109,5,"Onon ne on ndewatah Mbo ndewat Mi O ko Oon woni Alla."
  109,6,"Woodanii on diine mon mbo pepindaniɗon pittaali mon, woodanii kam diine mbo Alla tellini e Am."
